title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-3.1 - Emission limits
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-3.1 - Emission limits

State Regulations

Commencing in model year 2006, each manufacturer's fleet
of personal watercraft engines produced and delivered for sale in New York
shall not exceed the emission limits set forth in California Code of

Regulations, section 2442 (see Table 1, section
200.9
of this Title) using New York
specific vehicle numbers. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
210-3.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
